818
00:50:45,495 --> 00:50:46,795
How about...

819
00:50:48,210 --> 00:50:49,860
Luke Armstrong?

820
00:50:54,980 --> 00:50:56,280
That one...

821
00:50:56,740 --> 00:50:59,520
Thomas Sharp. A waste of a life.

822
00:50:59,550 --> 00:51:01,670
He grew up round
