914
00:56:22,540 --> 00:56:24,130
In your home?

915
00:56:24,780 --> 00:56:26,080
Yeah.

916
00:56:26,590 --> 00:56:29,840
I keep thinking that
if I close my eyes...

917
00:56:29,850 --> 00:56:31,150
