1035
01:05:37,520 --> 01:05:40,010
And along comes Lily.

1036
01:05:40,990 --> 01:05:43,310
Oh, I bet you were
more than flattered.

1037
01:05:43,920 --> 01:05:46,600
- What nearly-man wouldn't be?
